        },
        {
          "text": "Staffs here are very kind and supportive for student improvement.",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our college have inside stores and cafe where I can spend time during break hours.",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college uses design thinking as a main curriculum and it helps students to innovate a lot of new solutions",
          "name": "Lakshana Sree",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college emphasis on student talent rather than any other thing",
          "name": "Lakshana Sree",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our library.there is one class in our timetable for library.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The placements in my college is really good and average placement percentage is 85",
          "name": "KIRISHANTH G S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Another remarkable trait of my college is the DT team and it's methodology.",
          "name": "KIRISHANTH G S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are so many friendly staffs. And now the regulation was updated so you will learn new things which I' didn't learn. It will be helfull for your career.",
